original_title: Dr. Quinn Medicine Woman: The Movie
overview: As Colorado Springs' Commisioner, Sully opposes a deal to mine for copper to make electricity. In order to sway Sully's decision, Mr. Garrick threatens Sully. Sully and Michaela's daugther, Katie, is then kidnapped while the town celebrates Michaela's birthday. The search for Katie takes Sully, Micheala, and their friends on an adventure through Mexico that is filled with danger at every turn.
tagline: Her courage forged a new vision for the old west.
title: Dr. Quinn Medicine Woman: The Movie
